comments: Caruso (CHI) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Mathurin (IND), which affects his driving shot attempt.
Hield (IND) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Caruso's (CHI) body during his steal attempt.
Caruso (CHI) establishes himself in McConnell's (IND) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Hield (IND) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from LaVine (CHI) during the driving shot attempt.
The ball ricochets off LaVine (CHI) after it is cleanly dislodged and he is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Pacers.
Caruso (CHI) initiates contact with Nesmith (IND) that dislodges Nesmith (IND) as the pick is set.
Hield (IND) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Nesmith (IND) is adjusting to DeRozan's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Nesmith (IND) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact with DeRozan (CHI), which alters his driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Mathurin's (IND) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Turner (IND) avoids making contact with Vucevic's (CHI) arm as he contests the dunk attempt.
Nesmith (IND) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
LaVine (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Nesmith (IND).
LaVine (CHI) swings the ball from side to side and marginal contact occurs as McConnell (IND) retracts his hands from LaVine's path.
McConnell (IND) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes more than one step before releasing his dribble.
White (CHI) makes contact with Hield's (IND) face as he commits a take foul.
Hield (IND) legally contests Caruso's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
